Convert the CeleryKubernetesExecutor to a BaseExecutor.

@dstandish Should fix what you mentionned in https://github.com/apache/airflow/commit/42c30724d30e30f82cfc1c517f3c1d4d1e509747#r92580676

We have to `#type: ignore[override]` for now as mypy doesn't allow to override attribute with properties yet (even if getter and setter are both correctly implemented). This is only available in `0.991` https://github.com/python/mypy/commit/40dd719a536589d375ce8ef6cf5f9c6588bbea29. If you have a workaround to avoid this, don't hesitate :)

